This is the readme file for the Arduino PHP Agent


To use with your Arduino and Ethernet Shield, simply follow the next steps:


 1) Configure the MAC, ip, mask and gw variables with a valid settings to assign to the Arduino in the sketch.pde file

 2) Set the IP address to the Apache WEB server on which the agent.php will be deployed, in the sketch.pde file

 3) Copy agent.php and config.php to that Apache www directory or Vhost

 4) Go to http://ip:port/agent.php and enjoy



